{"tid":733031,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔敢再鍾意人係未真？","createTime":"2018-07-07T12:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T10:17:14.000Z","uid":169676,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"484ea6d67e083503447cd42119d7827ca133f372","tid":733031,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"我真係驚會忘記唔到佢<br />\n佢係我腦入面<br />\n發夢又見到<br />\n見到相似嘅人又會諗起佢<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線架咩！！<br />\n點解鍾意人都會咁撚折磨架？？？？<br />\n<br />\n拜托自己生性啲<br />\n唔好再咁上心鍾意其他人啦<br />\n真係好攞命囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有女搵我<br />\n我實會答<br />\n不了，我曾經愛上咗一個女仔<br />\n但有緣無分<br />\n彼此由朋友變返做陌生人<br />\n互不相干<br />\n最痛係我仲未忘記到佢<br />\n搞到我生不如死<br />\n所以我唔會再愛上其他人架啦<br />\n放過我啦好嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有食言<br />\n天打雷劈！！！！"},{"pid":"1dc325209cbd7659693af023579055ae942d3192","tid":733031,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ac131db543828c783a5000363905a4959b18579","tid":733031,"uid":169676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc325209cbd7659693af023579055ae942d3192","tid":733031,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:20:57.000Z","msg":"我寜願我一出世就係大陸仔<br />\n咁我就唔會遇上佢！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5b41e169e24bb73365972d651c5e1ef66c05a2","tid":733031,"uid":96482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ac131db543828c783a5000363905a4959b18579","tid":733031,"uid":169676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc325209cbd7659693af023579055ae942d3192","tid":733031,"uid":21423,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07